overview: These girls know that when a client gets cold feet there's one sure way to get him to do exactly what you want; let him pound that sweet real estate between your legs! Watch as 4 determined young real estate agents do everything they can to get that commission, and getting fucked is just an added bonus. Whether you're buying or selling, these girls will get it done!
tagline: "Always be closing" is a salespersons mantra, but these girls believe in "always be opening...their legs!"
title: Desperate Real Estate Agents 3
